title: Grosses Engelhorn
text: The Grosses Engelhorn is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the <a href="Bernese%20Alps">Bernese Alps</a>, located west of <a href="Innertkirchen">Innertkirchen</a> in the <a href="Bernese%20Oberland">Bernese Oberland</a>. It is one of the highest summits of the "Engelhörner", the chain between the Reichenbachtal and the Urbachtal.
